QuestData.Title: Rescuing the Expedition
QuestData.Description: The last members of my expedition are somewhere in here. We're going to need the knowledge they've gathered and their skills if we're to have any chance at defeating the naga.$B$BSee if you can find Earthbinder Rayge and Windcaller Claw, and make sure they're ok.
QuestData.LogDescription: Discover what happened to Earthbinder Rayge and Windcaller Claw. Then, return to Watcher Jhang.
QuestData.RewardText: Soon we'll all be together again, and I owe it all to you!$B$BWe'll bring the naga down before you know it, they don't stand a chance!
